Reliable & Professional
N3 Carpentry was founded on the tradition of our families values.   Our family of three is committed to building a business based on a foundation of integrity.  When you have a project we are committed to delivering premier customer service with quality products that are second to none.  We fully understand our industry, and we know having confidence in your contractor means everything.  Welcome to the Nimeth family! 

Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed!
It is our highest priority to get the job done right and within your budget. We strive to save you both time and money by combining our 20 years of experience. We've built our reputation on using the highest quality products and our dedication to delivering exceptional client service.  All workmanship is guaranteed for 60 days. Red Seal Canadian Ministry Certified. Licensed & Insured.
